  m_text: See those time controls? You can pause time, play normally, or speed things
    up! Your crops grow over time, and there's a day-night cycle. During the day,
    you farm and build. At night... well, that's when the wolves come. But don't
    worry - I've made the days extra long for this tutorial so you have plenty of
    time to learn!
